cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper is about using deep learning to assess cancer risk in CT lung screening, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE) sub-categories. The paper also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) in terms of interpreting the radiologist reports.
